1999 Apertura Playoffs

Quarterfinals

First Legs
[Nov 30]
Carcha         1-0 Municipal
Sacachispas    1-1 Comunicaciones 
[Dec 1]
Coban          0-0 Aurora
Universidad    0-0 Antigua

Second Legs [Dec 4]
Municipal      3-1 Carcha
Comunicaciones 3-1 Sacachispas 
Aurora         2-3 Coban   
Antigua        1-1 Universidad 

Semifinals 

First Legs
[Dec 7, 8]
Coban          2-1 Municipal
Universidad    0-1 Comunicaciones

Second Legs
[Dec 10, 11]
Municipal      3-1 Coban
Comunicaciones 3-1 Universidad

Final 

First Leg [Dec 14]
Comunicaciones 1-1 Municipal

Second Leg [Dec 18]
Municipal      1-2 Comunicaciones

Comunicaciones winners Apertura.

* 2000 Clausura Playoffs


Quarterfinals

First Legs
[May 13]
Aurora         0-3 Coban
[May 14]
Universidad    0-1 Comunicaciones
Antigua        0-2 Municipal
Santa Lucia    1-0 Carcha

Second Legs [May 21]
Coban          5-1 Aurora
Comunicaciones 3-1 Universidad
Municipal      3-0 Antigua
Carcha         0-1 Santa Lucia

Semifinals 

First Legs [May 24]
Santa Lucia    0-1 Comunicaciones
Coban          1-1 Municipal

Second Legs [May 28]
Comunicaciones 3-1 Santa Lucia
Municipal      3-1 Coban

Final

First Leg [May 31]
Municipal      0-1 Comunicaciones

Second Leg [Jun 4]
Comunicaciones 0-2 Municipal

Municipal winners Clausura.

NB: no playoff between winners Apertura and Clausura; Comunicaciones and
    Municipal both won 1 championship 1999/2000.




* 2000 Apertura


Quarterfinals

First Legs [Dec 13]
Universidad    1-4 Comunicaciones
Cobán          0-2 Municipal
Zacapa         2-1 Marquense
Antigua        1-1 Xelajú

Second Legs
[Dec 16]
Comunicaciones 3-1 Universidad
Xelajú         3-0 Antigua
[Dec 17]
Municipal      3-0 Cobán
Marquense      1-1 Zacapa

Semifinals

First Legs [Jan 10]
Zacapa         1-1 Comunicaciones
Xelajú         0-0 Municipal

Second Legs [Jan 13]
Comunicaciones 4-1 Zacapa
Municipal      1-0 Xelajú

Final

First Leg [Jan 17]
Municipal      0-0 Comunicaciones

Second Leg [Jan 20]
Comunicaciones 1-1 Municipal

Municipal winners on away goal (though both matches played in the same
stadium, Mateo Flores in Cd. de Guatemala!)

